data.description: 'CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS'.  Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a family and dog-friendly community! This impeccable 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers not just a house, but a haven for comfortable living. Meticulously maintained by a single owner, this residence exudes warmth and care in every corner.As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the thoughtful design of the Ryder floor plan featuring a desirable split floor plan, providing both privacy and convenience for your family. The spacious living areas create an inviting atmosphere, perfect for both relaxation and entertainment.With four generously sized bedrooms, everyone in the family will have their own retreat. The master suite boasts a private en-suite bathroom, ensuring a serene space for relaxation. The additional three bedrooms provide flexibility for guests, an office, or a playroom - the possibilities are endless.This charming residence is ideally situated within sight of the bay, allowing you easy access to walk on the trail to watch the sunrise or sunset, enjoy your favorite water sport or walk your dog. Additionally, it's a short walk to the community pool, making it easy for you to take a refreshing dip or gather with friends and neighbors on sunny afternoons.Location is key, and this home has it all. Commuting is a breeze with Tyndall Air Force Base only 10 minutes away, Panama City just 15 minutes down the road, and the pristine shores of Mexico Beach just a 20-minute drive away. You'll have the best of both worlds, with proximity to work, city amenities, and the beautiful Gulf Coast beaches.Don't miss this opportunity to make this one-owner, meticulously maintained home your own. It's not just a house; it's a place where cherished memories are waiting to be created. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm of this family-friendly community for yourself!
